race.comment: Scratchings have taken a few of the better chances out. Hard to go past COOL PANELS (7) now who is fitter for two runs in. Was a fresh-up winner then a solid fourth in what has proven a hot form race. Fitter again and worth noting is unbeaten here from two tries at the distance. Hard to beat. MR WANDJI (5) has been freshened since a last start win at Chinchilla. This tougher but going well and looks a leading chance again. BULSARA (2) has a big weight but senior rider goes aboard and among the chances.  LOOSE UNIT (4) is fitter for two runs back and placed last time, albeit in easier. Has won third-up and should be at top now.
